tip.text: Had chorizo pizza and pasta.  Both are super yummy and extremely satisfying after a long day of skiing.  Went two days in a row!
Great view of Matterhorn, lovely, cozy and bright!
Octopus starter is simple, tender and yummy.  Pizzas are delicious, also tried langoustine pasta that was very different and generous.
Delicious pizzas - medium sized but thick and light with delicious choices of toppings.
Lovely place, short walking distance to center.
Definitely satisfied my cravings.. they have banh beo!! .. yum!
Hazelnut & lemon meringue tasted divine & very fresh! Could be slightly bigger sized. Cupcakes all look very promising and the red velvet was super moist. Party treats layout looked irresistible!
Best hidden bar in Wan Chai.  Unpretentious, relaxed and original.
